From cc294bf83686597605530adc53b282ed1c2fe4d4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 16 Jul 2025 15:23:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP:wifi:mac80211:Add per-TID RX stats support with drop
 reasons

Improve the RX statistics reporting in the mac80211 subsystem by adding
detailed counters for various RX packet reasons and drop statistics for
specific TIDs.

Patch Dependency : None

Signed-off-by: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
Co-Developed by: Girish Kumar M P <gmp@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 include/net/mac80211.h     |   1 +
 net/mac80211/drop.h        |  60 ++++++++
 net/mac80211/ieee80211_i.h |  12 ++
 net/mac80211/rx.c          | 274 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
 4 files changed, 319 insertions(+), 28 deletions(-)

--- a/include/net/mac80211.h
+++ b/include/net/mac80211.h
@@ -1778,6 +1778,7 @@ struct ieee80211_rx_status {
 	u8 zero_length_psdu_type;
 	u8 link_valid:1, link_id:4;
